{"tid":2435802,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★至少17人打科興疫苗現副作用　大部分頭暈心悸","createTime":"2021-03-06T14:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-06T15:15:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f44dade010a0bdf1587a96a5c522c44c66462ea3","tid":2435802,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:01:52.000Z","msg":"香港由上周五(2月26日)起的一個星期內，有6.15萬人已接種科興疫苗，出現17宗不良事故，而嚴重或非預期事故比率是0.02%，屬於預期之內。至於該17人的病徵，大部分都是頭暈和心悸，經治療後已經康復。他又說，第4波疫情已經受控，以瑪麗醫院為例，現時只有2、3名確診者仍留醫，相信他們很快可以出院，而公營體系亦能騰出人手，協助推行疫苗接種計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210306/bkn-20210306115204632-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20210306%2Fbkn-20210306115204632-0306_00822_001.html&d=vOSJ0XARgdQWnSR9BVy1n%2F3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=a39ecfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20210306/bkn-20210306115204632-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"e81d782bc80dcbb9938cbae8f372d3adfb2ad949","tid":2435802,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:01:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb16403189231b7fc675708fb6f81eab4929ea1","tid":2435802,"uid":211994,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:02:49.000Z","msg":"打支針！（嘩！）厚禮是即刻出殯！"},{"pid":"af533ac199efa1563a0837f6e9fec2cfc1092190","tid":2435802,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%